description: This subtly detailed, traditional sleeve provides a streamlined option that fits within any anyone’s comfort zone.  The wrap construction cradles your netbook in substantial foam padding, and thoughtful details add hints of sophisticated styling.  Slide this sleek sleeve easily into your briefcase, backpack, tote or other bag.
title: Case Logic LAPST-107 6 - 7-Inch Kindle Fire/Tablet/eBook Sleeve (Black)
